title: Botswana Consumer Spending
description: Consumer Spending in Botswana increased to 20241.40 BWP Million in the second quarter of 2022 from 20178.90 BWP Million in the first quarter of 2022. Consumer Spending in Botswana averaged 9887.31 BWP Million from 2003 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 20423.40 BWP Million in the fourth quarter of 2021 and a record low of 3381.10 BWP Million in the second quarter of 2003. This page provides - Botswana Consumer Spending - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Office, Botswana
